message.body: Hey- am I going crazy, or are you not on Facebook anymore?
I deactivated it a week or two ago. I found myself looking at it too much.
Ah! Okay :-) By the way, have you ever been to lighthouse point park? I went yesterday. It was pretty decent!
I have been meaning to go there (for like 2 years!) but haven't yet
Let me know if you ever want to check it out. I have my new haven beach parking pass now :-)
Yes! A bit rocky, but you can swim in the lifeguard section
Ohh didnt even know that. Let me know when u plan on going again. The next month or so is crazy for me (vacation/bridal showers/bachelorette parties/
weddings) so I think the next weekend I am here is the first weekend in august. Stressed just thinking about it.
